original_title: The Newbridge Tourism Board Presents: "We're Newbridge, We're Comin' To Get Ya!"
overview: Based on the popular Best Show of WFMU, comedy duo Scharpling and Wurster adapt a few of their most popular characters into a tourism advertisement for the fictional city of Newbridge, NJ.
title: The Newbridge Tourism Board Presents: "We're Newbridge, We're Comin' To Get Ya!"
